# 🧠 Resume Ranker AI (FastAPI)

A simple, production-ready API that ranks resume PDFs based on a job description using **Sentence Transformer** embeddings and **cosine similarity**. Built using **FastAPI**.

## 🚀 Features
- Upload multiple PDF resumes
- Input job description text
- Get ranked similarity scores using transformer embeddings
- Auto docs via Swagger UI

## 🗂️ Tech Stack
- Python
- FastAPI
- Sentence-Transformers (MiniLM)
- PyPDF2
- Scikit-learn

## 🔧 How to Run

1. Clone this repo
2. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt